           <span \n                class=\"whitespace-nowrap\"\n            >Get Started Easily<\/span>\n            <span class=\"text-green\">&gt;&gt;<\/span>\n                    <span \n                class=\"whitespace-nowrap\"\n            >Drive Security Innovation<\/span>\n            <span class=\"text-green\">&gt;&gt;<\/span>\n                    <span \n                class=\"whitespace-nowrap\"\n            >Stay Ahead of Threats<\/span>\n            <span class=\"text-green\">&gt;&gt;<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group mb-50 mt-35\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center mb-22\">Get more of what you want with Prowler<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group c-card-grid c-card-grid--2-up js-tailcraft-animate max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--1 delay-0 pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"76\" height=\"52\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cloud-lock-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-landscape\" alt=\"cloud lock icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Open Cloud Security<\/h4>\n                <p>Prowler Open Source and Prowler Hosted (SaaS) empower the Open Cloud Security movement by providing transparent, community-driven security solutions.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--2 delay-250 pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/lightbulb-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-square\" alt=\"lightbulb icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Collaborative Innovation<\/h4>\n                <p>The Prowler community drives continuous improvement, ensuring the platform adapts to evolving cloud services, features, and security threats.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--3 delay-500 pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"45\" height=\"84\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/flow-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-portrait\" alt=\"flow icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Flexibility and Customization<\/h4>\n                <p>The Prowler community drives continuous improvement, ensuring the platform adapts to evolving cloud services, features, and security threats.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--4 delay-750 pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/cog-with-turning-arrows-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-square\" alt=\"cog with turning arrows icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Efficiency and Automation<\/h4>\n                <p>Prowler reduces manual overhead through automated security assessments, compliance checks, and threat detection, saving time and resources.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group e-lines-y e-break-out-to-lines\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns e-accent-divider py-32 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Prowler is Open Source<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"max-w-96\">Prowler is an Open Cloud Security platform that&#8217;s as dynamic as your cloud environment. It revolutionizes cloud security with Open Source flexibility, empowering you to secure cloud environments in a way that&#8217;s best for your business &#8211; whatever that looks like.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex justify-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full flex justify-center items-center e-screenshot max-w-2xl\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler-screenshot-scan-overview-detailed-trimmed@2x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-729\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group mb-50 mt-35\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center mb-22\">When to Use Prowler <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group c-card-grid c-card-grid--2-up js-tailcraft-animate max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div \n    class=\"block--text-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl count--1 remainder--1 delay-0 lg:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Security Engineers<\/h4>\n                <p>Prowler Open Source is perfect for security engineers who want to dig into the CLI and run it on their own to deeply understand the inner workings of the security checks and customize them as per their organization&#8217;s needs.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--text-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl count--2 remainder--0 delay-500 lg:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Hands-on Experimentation<\/h4>\n                <p>The open-source nature of Prowler allows security engineers to experiment with the code, contribute to the project, and collaborate with the wider community to enhance the security capabilities.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--text-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl count--3 remainder--1 delay-1000 lg:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Integrating with Existing Workflows<\/h4>\n                <p>Security engineers can seamlessly integrate Prowler Open Source into their existing security toolchain, scripts, and workflows, automating security assessments and monitoring as part of their DevSecOps practices.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--text-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl count--4 remainder--0 delay-1500 lg:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Customized Reporting<\/h4>\n                <p>Prowler Open Source gives security engineers the flexibility to generate customized reports and visualizations that align with their organization&#8217;s specific security requirements and compliance needs.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--text-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl count--5 remainder--1 delay-2000 lg:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Community Engagement<\/h4>\n                <p>By using and contributing to Prowler Open Source, security engineers can actively participate in the vibrant community, share insights, and help shape the future of cloud security tools.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--text-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl count--6 remainder--0 delay-2500 lg:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Benefit from Intuitive Controls<\/h4>\n                <p>Prowler Cloud provides easy-to-use, click-based controls that enable you to quickly navigate, filter, and analyze your cloud security data, making it simple to identify and address vulnerabi